{"title":"State Bicycle Co. Carbon Monster Fork V2 Includes Flip Chip For Added Versatility","link":"https://bikerumor.com/state-bicycle-carbon-monster-fork-v2/","date":1726688367000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-hero-jpeg.webp\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" alt=\"(Photos / State Bicycles)\" /></p>\n<p>Hot on the heels of the release of their super affordable <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/state-bicycle-co-titanium-all-road-bike/\" target=\"_blank\">titanium All Road</a> bike, <a href=\"https://www.statebicycle.com/\" target=\"_blank\">State Bicycles</a> has released a new, equally affordable <a href=\"https://www.statebicycle.com/collections/frames/products/state-bicycle-co-carbon-fiber-monster-gravel-fork\" target=\"_blank\">v2 Carbon Monster</a> fork. The new fork is equipped with a flip-chip, adding to its versatility, and making it a great addition to your current gravel or bikepacking steed.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-full-fork-side-jpeg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-full-fork-side-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"State Bikes v2 Carbon Monster Fork full fork side\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-full-fork-side-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-full-fork-side-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-full-fork-side-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-full-fork-side-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-full-fork-side-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-full-fork-side-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a><figcaption>(Photos / State Bicycles)</figcaption></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-full-carbon-steerer-jpeg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-full-carbon-steerer-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"State Bikes v2 Carbon Monster Fork full carbon steerer\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-full-carbon-steerer-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-full-carbon-steerer-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-full-carbon-steerer-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-full-carbon-steerer-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-full-carbon-steerer-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-full-carbon-steerer-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>It’s made just like the original version, with the “highest-grade carbon fiber, engineered to take on the toughest terrains while keeping your ride light and agile”. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-flip-chip-up-close-jpeg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-flip-chip-up-close-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"State Bikes v2 Carbon Monster Fork flip chip up close\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-flip-chip-up-close-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-flip-chip-up-close-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-flip-chip-up-close-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-flip-chip-up-close-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-flip-chip-up-close-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-flip-chip-up-close-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a><figcaption>Flip Chip set at 55.5mm</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-flip-chip-jpeg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-flip-chip-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"State Bikes v2 Carbon Monster Fork flip chip\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-flip-chip-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-flip-chip-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-flip-chip-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-flip-chip-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-flip-chip-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-flip-chip-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a><figcaption>Flip Chip set at 49mm</figcaption></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The biggest difference between the two forks is the addition of the flip chip to the v2. The flip chip will change the rake of the fork from 49mm to 55.5mm. Flipping the chip will change the geometry of your bike by allowing the rider to adjust for particular terrain.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-full-bike-55.5mm-jpeg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-full-bike-55.5mm-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"State Bikes v2 Carbon Monster Fork full bike 55.5mm\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-full-bike-55.5mm-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-full-bike-55.5mm-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-full-bike-55.5mm-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-full-bike-55.5mm-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-full-bike-55.5mm-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-full-bike-55.5mm-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a><figcaption>Flip chip at 55.5mm</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-full-bike-49mm-jpeg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-full-bike-49mm-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"State Bikes v2 Carbon Monster Fork full bike 49mm\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-full-bike-49mm-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-full-bike-49mm-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-full-bike-49mm-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-full-bike-49mm-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-full-bike-49mm-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-full-bike-49mm-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a><figcaption>Flip Chip set at 49mm</figcaption></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-wheel-49mm-jpeg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-wheel-49mm-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"State Bikes v2 Carbon Monster Fork wheel 49mm\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-wheel-49mm-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-wheel-49mm-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-wheel-49mm-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-wheel-49mm-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-wheel-49mm-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-wheel-49mm-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a><figcaption>Flip chip at 49mm</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>For instance, the 49mm offset is ideal for making stability and control a priority while riding technical trails. It allows for the bike to be confidently ridden on rough gravel, tight, and twisty singletrack, or techy descents. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-wheel-55.5mm-jpeg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-wheel-55.5mm-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"State Bikes v2 Carbon Monster Fork wheel 55.5mm\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-wheel-55.5mm-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-wheel-55.5mm-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-wheel-55.5mm-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-wheel-55.5mm-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-wheel-55.5mm-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-wheel-55.5mm-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a><figcaption>Flip Chip at 55.5mm</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Flipping the chip to the 55.5mm position gives the rider a more stable, smoother ride. By lengthening the wheelbase of your steed, you increase straight-line stability. This would be ideal for long-distance bikepacking trips or fast gravel roads. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-thru-axle-jpeg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-thru-axle-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"State Bikes v2 Carbon Monster Fork thru axle\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-thru-axle-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-thru-axle-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-thru-axle-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-thru-axle-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-thru-axle-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/State-Bikes-v2-Carbon-Monster-Fork-thru-axle-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Ready for adventure? Well, the fork also has adventure designed right into it. It carries a ton of mounting points and will accommodate tires up to 700c x 55mm or 650b x 2.3″ (49mm setting) and 700c x 58mm or 650b x 2.4″ (55.5mm setting)</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>v2 Carbon Monster Fork Retail and Features</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Retail; $299</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Material: </strong>High-grade carbon fiber</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Steerer:</strong> Full carbon, 1 1/8″ – 1 1/2″ tapered</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Dropout:</strong> Carbon fiber, compatible with 12 x100mm thru-axle (M12 thread pitch)</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Brakes: </strong>Flat mount disc-brake interface</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Thru-Axle: </strong>Included</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://www.statebicycle.com/\" target=\"_blank\">StateBicycle.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/state-bicycle-carbon-monster-fork-v2/\">State Bicycle Co. Carbon Monster Fork V2 Includes Flip Chip For Added Versatility</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Ron Frazelle","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"ea64bc9e91186aabd41daa171ca7bc2bb771400c58093238ee612aab5dbb7b72","category":"Cycling"}